page.title: 15BIRD WATCH
page.content:
We did two 3 hour birdwatches.
1. Berry Farm 4th July 1985. Birds seen: Wood pigeon, Jackdaw, Magpie, Swallow, House Martin, Sparrow Hawk, Rook, Goldfinch, Chiff chaff, Willow warbler, Wren, Blue tit, Great tit, House sparrow, Skylark, Buzzard, Pheasant, Snipe, Robin, Blackbird, Swift, Chaffinch.
2a. Pitt Cottage 29.6.85 2-4 p.m. In addition to above - Yellowhammer, Sand martin, Nuthatch, Greenfinch.
2b. Trout Farm, Thornbury 4-5 p.m. In addition to above only a goldfinch chick. Kingfishers are often seen at the farm.
